lines: 1. Ringra namiyoi,remba nochwer ni in;Nawaroi adiere teko mar Satan;Yandi remba nochwer ni in,ang`o mimiyo an?Yandi remba nochwer ni in,ang`o mimiyo an?
2. Naweyo od Wuora,gi duong` ma nie polo;Nachandora e piny,mondo anyisi yo;Yandi achandora ni in,ang`o mitiyona?Yandi achandora ni in,ang`o mitiyona?
3. Bura noloyoi,to an nayudo chwat;Natho e Kalwari,mondo akony jopiny;Yandi atho mond` awari;ang`o mitimona?Yandi atho mond` awari;ang`o mitimona?
